  "budget_usd": 5,

  "notes": "P4 enters at ODK (not PIK or EEK). Flow: DCR → INR → PMR → ODK→EEK transition → KER (Path B citing PMR corrective actions). Test stops after KER freeze. Note: EEK may not have entry-from-odk.md — log as framework gap if sherpa struggles with the handoff."
}
